{"tid":431131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★養兒防老夢想破滅 ］母：畀唔起$3000家用　禁用洗衣機","createTime":"2017-10-10T11:58:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-17T09:43:18.000Z","uid":19454,"like":109,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"d8031a6fa0ae1339ed2b49e2c5e31cb3b0d271f6","tid":431131,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T11:58:50.000Z","msg":"facebook專頁「CUHK Secrets」今午3時發文，投稿的網民稱自己是今年其中一科「乞食科」的畢業生，至今未找到工作，媽媽卻要求他每月給3000元家用，他因沒有工作而付不起。作為「失業生」，該網民表示在家中想使用洗衣機時，竟然見到洗衣機的插頭被加上鎖頭，不能插上插頭取電。從投稿的照片可見，一個3腳插頭被扣上一把鎖，導致不能完全插進插座，變相無法取電使用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/894831/xlarge/cf70aa7355b731ce006017b6c9c26fa3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F894831%2Fxlarge%2Fcf70aa7355b731ce006017b6c9c26fa3.jpg&h=7cf9041c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/熱話/124853/網民稱乞食科畢業無工開-畀唔起-3000家用-遭母鎖洗衣機禁用\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%2F124853%2F%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%A8%B1%E4%B9%9E%E9%A3%9F%E7%A7%91%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E7%84%A1%E5%B7%A5%E9%96%8B-%E7%95%80%E5%94%94%E8%B5%B7-3000%E5%AE%B6%E7%94%A8-%E9%81%AD%E6%AF%8D%E9%8E%96%E6%B4%97%E8%A1%A3%E6%A9%9F%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8&d=g9ZhlBacktmsfUCJb49Fiy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=a3aafc8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/熱話/124853/網民稱乞食科畢業無工開-畀唔起-3000家用-遭母鎖洗衣機禁用</a>"},{"pid":"d733f534bf9e8195b7223cc99fd8f5231d4cf87f","tid":431131,"uid":19454,"like":137,"dislike":1,"score":136,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T11:59:20.000Z","msg":"投資失利<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6e12015be2ffd5aa65b8827b662e1a673513ab","tid":431131,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T11:59:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb0853c9fd94735f122f02645cdc8806e373ef7c"